    "about": {
        "sectionTitle": "About Me",
        "paragraphs": [
            "I am an Information Technology professional with over 20 years of experience in web systems and mobile application development. Currently, I work as an IT Analyst at Universidade Federal do Pampa (Unipampa), contributing directly to critical institutional systems.",
            "I have strong experience in software architecture, data modeling, and development standards definition. Between 2016 and 2019, I worked in a technical leadership role, coordinating teams, leading projects, organizing processes, and mentoring developers.",
            "My background includes the development of large-scale systems, such as ERPs with dozens of integrated modules, as well as modern mobile applications using Flutter, always focused on performance, scalability, and code quality."
